  <title translate="true">ColumnCount</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">ColumnCount</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height:2.0;"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">ColumnCount</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">For MODFLOW, PHAST, and WellFootprint models, </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">ColumnCount</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> returns the number of column boundaries in the grid, which equals the number of nodes in the X direction for PHAST models and the number of cells plus 1 for MODFLOW models. For SUTRA and MODFLOW 6 DISV models, </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">ColumnCount</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> returns the number of nodes, elements, or cells in the top view of the model.</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
